Load a new instance of a module.

Parameters:
channel -
moduleName -
userAgent -
url - top-level URL of the main page, null if using an old plugin
tabKey - opaque key of the tab, may be empty if the plugin can't distinguish tabs or null if using an old plugin
sessionKey - opaque key for this session, null if using an old plugin
userAgentIcon - byte array containing an icon (which fits within 24x24) representing the user agent or null if unavailable
Returns:
a TreeLogger to use for the module's logs, or null if the module load failed
